1.route-policy工具
配置acl
(1)acl
acl 2000
rule permit source 172.16.1.0 0.0.0.0

使用route-policy
route-policy RP permit node 10
if-match acl 2000
apply cost 10

ospf 1
import-route direct route-policy RP

(2)ip-prefix
ip-prefix(在过滤相同网络号不同淹码的包时使用)
ip ip-prefix deny name 192.168.0.0 24 
ip ip-prefix permit 0.0.0.0 0 less-equal 32 //permit any
route-policy name permit node 10
if-match ip-prefix name

2.filter-policy(对入和出进行过滤,但是不过滤lsa,只是在lsdb转化为路由表时过滤)
filter-policy ip-prefix export direct(直连方式导入的路由转发时过滤掉)
filter-policy ip-prefix export ospf(ospf方式导入的路由转发时过滤掉)
filter-policy ip-prefix import ospf(ospf方式导入的路由过滤掉)
